name: FIRST PICK NATE
description:
INSIDER TRADING HAS NEVER LOOKED SO STUPID :)

On September 15th 2021 Nate Chastain was accused of insider trading after screenshots of his wallet transactions where shared around twitter. You could see he had been purchasing NFT's before they where publicly available, then flipping them sometimes minutes after official drops.. A day later he tweeted at another minting platform asking for a job after having handed in his resignation at Opensea.. What a guy..
